Beneath the tower of Barad-d√ªr, a ravine of death and decay simmers and stagnates. There, the Dead swarm in great numbers throughout the pools of Angathrai. Fell summoners use cursed runes to call forth the Dead to do their bidding. You should defeat the creatures that wander among the pools of Angathrai.
The Dead swarm in great numbers throughout the sunken ravine of Angathrai.
Angathrai can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat foes at Angathrai.
You defeated many foes at Angathrai and halted the summoning of fell spirits. Your efforts upon the Shadowfells will not go unnoticed, and must surely hinder the plans of Sauron.
